OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781247870
OL,3,CDan Jarvis appointed as new Defence
OL,4,CSecretary
OL,6,FDan Jarvis has been appointed as the
OL,7,Fnew defence secretary following John
OL,8,FHealey's resignation earlier on
OL,9,FThursday in a dispute over military
OL,10,Ffunding.
OL,12,FThe Barnsley North MP has served as
OL,13,Fsecurity minister since 2024 in the
OL,14,FHome Office.
OL,16,FA former soldier, Jarvis was first
OL,17,Felected as an MP in 2011 and held a
OL,18,Fvariety of shadow front bench roles
OL,19,Fbefore serving on the Joint Committee
OL,20,Fon the National Security Strategy in
OL,21,F2017.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
