OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781247870
OL,3,CDan Jarvis appointed as new Defence
OL,4,CSecretary
OL,6,FIn 2018, he was elected as the first
OL,7,FMayor of South Yorkshire, and after
OL,8,Fleaving the mayoralty, he was
OL,9,Fappointed Shadow Security Minister in
OL,10,FSeptember 2023.
OL,12,FIn a statement released after Jarvis'
OL,13,Fappointment, Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,14,FStarmer said he was pleased to make
OL,15,Fthe appointment, as the government
OL,16,Fworks to "meet the growing threats
OL,17,Ffacing our country."
OL,26,@xD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
