OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781247870
OL,3,CDan Jarvis appointed as new Defence
OL,4,CSecretary
OL,6,FHealey said the prime minister has
OL,7,F"been unable... to commit the
OL,8,Fresources that the nation needs to
OL,9,Fdefend the country" and that he has
OL,10,F"no other option" but to resign.
OL,12,FHe added: "I am being forced to make a
OL,13,Fdecision that would reduce the
OL,14,Freadiness of our Forces and increase
OL,15,Fthe risk to personnel on operations,
OL,16,Fand could make the country less safe."
