CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781247870
OL,3,CDan Jarvis appointed as new Defence
OL,4,CSecretary
OL,6,FHe added that "demands on defence have
OL,7,Fincreased still further", pointing to
OL,8,Fthe Iran war, threats from Russia in
OL,9,Fthe High North, and escalation in the
OL,10,FUkraine conflict.
OL,12,FHis resignation was shortly followed
OL,13,Fby that of his Parliamentary Private
OL,14,FSecretary, Pamela Nash, and Armed
OL,15,FForces Minister Al Carns, the latter
OL,16,Fof whom laid into the government more
OL,17,Fbroadly, saying: "The machinery of
OL,18,Fgovernment itself has been left to
OL,19,Fdecay".
OL,26,@nD@OOUoD@XO]
